  "title": "Global Block Hardness",
  "description": "This mod makes breaking blocks easier or harder.",
  "body": "<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VBYVKRh/global-block-hardness.png\"></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> 📖About </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> This mod makes breaking blocks easier or harder. </span></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> 📘 How to use? </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 22px;\"> 1.12: </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> 1. Start the game<br>2. Open the <strong><em>config</em></strong> folder, located inside the game directory<br>3. Open <strong><em>globalblockhardness.cfg</em></strong> config file<br>4. Change the <strong><em>globalBlockHardnessMultiplier</em></strong> to your liking<br>5. Restart the game for changes to take effect. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: red; font-size: 22px;\"> 1.13+: </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> 1. Create or join a world.<br>2. Open the <strong><em>serverconfig</em></strong> folder located inside your world folder<br>3. Open <strong><em>globalblockhardness-server.toml</em></strong> config file<br>4. Change the <strong><em>globalBlockHardnessMultiplier</em></strong> to your liking<br>5. Enjoy 👌<br>Note: In 1.13.2, 1.14.2 and 1.14.3 you will also have to restart the world for changes to take effect! </span></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> 💡 FAQ's </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"> Q: Experiencing bugs/issues while using the mod?<br>A: Please, submit your bug/issue report <a href=\"https://github.com/darkorg69/global-block-hardness/issues\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">here</span></a>.<br><br>Q: Can I include this mod in my modpack?<br>A: Yes! </span></p>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 26px;\"> Make sure to check out my other mods 🤗 </span></p>\n<table style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-leveling\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/s1HMvbt/better-leveling.png\"> </a></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-punching\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/xDZbg47/better-punching.png\"> </a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-materials\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/CtGz93k/better-materials.png\"> </a></td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-durability\" rel=\"nofollow\"> <img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Mk2gxRm/better-durability.png\"> </a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%;\" src=\"https://i.ibb.co/q9ZCqmY/line.png\"></p>",
